Package com.microsoft.azure.sdk.iot.deps.serializer

Class FileUploadResponseParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.microsoft.azure.sdk.iot.deps.serializer.FileUploadResponseParser

  • public class FileUploadResponseParser
extends java.lang.Object
    Representation of a single container for the File Upload response with a Json deserializer. Ex of JSON format: { "correlationId": "somecorrelationid", "hostname": "contoso.azure-devices.net", "containerName": "testcontainer", "blobName": "test-device1/image.jpg", "sasToken": "1234asdfSAStoken" }
